:"48f4a3b87d559795dd46551616cdff82b92d3a06","tid":2369931,"uid":170666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />14日後"},{"pid":"3e81062c917f8d1838ce8aba52c365e78cf8f262","tid":2369931,"uid":170666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T11:21:30.000Z","msg":"有出廣告啦 2月7號起，逢星期日晚11點，港台電視31"},{"pid":"5ed33d165eff9d2f05c80d2c55d66bfb26e566a3","tid":2369931,"uid":170666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:37:14.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"996f67f6695849acdc75712b75445770001bca9d","tid":2369931,"uid":170666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:57:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/knowledgezone.rthk/videos/454449949255817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fknowledgezone.rthk%2Fvideos%2F454449949255817&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=a66cdcd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/knowledgezone.rthk/videos/454449949255817</a><br />\n【漫遊百科2021】返嚟喇 !!<br />\n新一輯《漫遊百科》返嚟喇 !!<br />\n今輯節目有 Will Or 柯煒林 同我地一齊學習。面對新冠肺炎疫情的影響，節目都加入網上直播講座，講座對象除了現場觀眾外，進一步擴大至無地域限制的網上觀眾，確實是知識分享無界限。<br />\n2月7號起，逢星期日晚11點，港台電視31<br />\n#漫遊百科<br />\n#講座<br />\n#新冠肺炎"},{"pid":"7095e0d9fa6d22bb5ad72d095aaf4eb68e0028d4","tid":2369931,"uid":170666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:58:01.000Z","msg":"【漫遊百科】一連12集節目，每集 Will Or 柯煒林會帶大家聽吓唔同範疇嘅講座，涉獵歷史、藝術、科學、哲學......等等嘅題目，希望做到「漫遊....百科！」<br />\n比住個優先場你地睇住先喇~<br />\n記住，記住，記住<br />\n星期日（2月7日）有得睇新一輯《漫遊百科》喇，大家記住收睇呀！！<br />\n===============<br />\n《#漫遊百科》，由2月7日起 11pm，#港台電視31 播出。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/knowledgezone2021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fknowledgezone2021&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=792cea2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/knowledgezone2021</a><br />\n#漫遊百科<br />\n#講座<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/knowledgezone.rthk/videos/413932920058938\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fknowledgezone.rthk%2Fvideos%2F413932920058938&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=c7538251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/knowledgezone.rthk/videos/413932920058938</a>"},{"pid":"f0083baa2b9c25bd68b91e69e608933c23d249b6","tid":2369931,"uid":170666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"2日後"},{"pid":"26db8052760cd96fd46590feb2dcf72bcc4928f0","tid":2369931,"uid":170666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T14:02:02.000Z","msg":"《漫遊百科》第一集，有Will Or 柯煒林同我地一齊學習。<br />\n今集李浩然博士會同大家講下油麻地戲院嘅建築特色同電影歷史嘅關係。<br />\n另外，會介紹一位模型改裝達人鍾潤德(豬膶)<br />\n，睇下佢點樣上網學自學燈光編程，喺疫情下都可以搵到自我增值嘅方法。<br />\n星期日晚11點 #港台電視31 播出。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/knowledgezone2021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fknowledgezone2021&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=792cea2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/knowledgezone2021</a><br />\n#漫遊百科<br />\n#講座<br />\n#電影 #戲院 #建築 #歷史<br />\n#燈神 #模型 #燈光 #編程<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/knowledgezone.rthk/videos/337541357460581\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fknowledgezone.rthk%2Fvideos%2F337541357460581&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=9e910cb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/knowledgezone.rthk/videos/337541357460581</a>"},{"pid":"b4f70933ce69e8c29f9913b2e7e0a9d2df424ea2","tid":2369931,"uid":170666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T04:56:02.000Z","msg":"this night"},{"pid":"ed90f9e7296381e4bdff3fa