8hh7p.jpg&h=9b0ea890&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8742583cf79c1cf3c6802dd64bae7133bcbac52","tid":2369931,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F7EgyFO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF7EgyFO.jpg&h=1089a42d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd046fb4d2562605b770c22568e41f2afa6d6f4c","tid":2369931,"uid":170666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:41:42.000Z","msg":"好認真講戲院 港台真係好盡責"},{"pid":"e167cca57d58b99b732482748adb8e70cd1eeea4","tid":2369931,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"hi will"},{"pid":"c95d9e15ac0fa4985fb1b24739e593bcc445007b","tid":2369931,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q1wZwyL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq1wZwyL.png&h=79c80b49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"037fb2935ef3ded45af3f8561ef13011b6ab583b","tid":2369931,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZYMV2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZYMV2c.jpg&h=12471890&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff29be345555b2d42c3c039b858457bec0732a9b","tid":2369931,"uid":170666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T13:32:47.000Z","msg":"【第二集：生態資源】漫遊百科今集同你講：小丑魚<br />\n「Nemo」、「海葵魚」、「新娘」同「番茄」都係 #小丑魚 嘅花名。大眾對小丑魚嘅印象大多停留喺動畫中可愛嘅形象，但對於佢地嘅種類、習性同生理結構又有幾多認識呢？<br />\n香港大學生態學及生物多樣性學系研究畢業生施駿龍，會介紹小丑魚鮮為人知嘅一面，包括女尊男卑嘅社會結構同兩性異形嘅生理特徵，亦會教大家分辨雄性同雌性小丑魚。<br />\n【網上學識】嘉道理農場暨植物園設立特備網站《#森林日常》，將大自然「upload」上網，俾大人同小朋友可以安在家中，感受大自然嘅美好。<br />\n#港台電視31 #漫遊百科 #生態資源 #大自然"},{"pid":"6e7aeac1cc328753692b57ba0b847248f6d98329","tid":2369931,"uid":170666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T13:33:10.000Z","msg":"喺水底遇過 #小丑魚 嘅朋友，應該唔會比佢可愛嘅外表呃到，因為其實佢係好鍾意咬人㗎！<br />\n第二集《漫遊百科》除咗有主持Will Or 柯煒林，仲邀請到Gomen施駿龍同大家分享小丑魚點解咁鍾意咬人，同埋佢哋嘅變性過程。<br />\n另外，仲會介紹嘉道理農場暨植物園教育部，點樣將大自然upload上網同大家分享。<br />\n星期日晚11點 #港台電視31 播出。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/knowledgezone2021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fknowledgezone2021&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=792cea2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/knowledgezone2021</a><br />\n#漫遊百科 #講座 #生態資源 #森林日常  #大自然<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/knowledgezone.rthk/videos/329740265060298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fknowledgezone.rthk%2Fvideos%2F329740265060298&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=6eec9890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/knowledgezone.rthk/videos/329740265060298</a>"},{"pid":"b7e14ec8f5a1840416353a30d126ef488bd5f24d","tid":2369931,"uid":170666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T13:08:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e4eee812306e41a9b3abf74899dcafe4c4f5686","tid":2369931,"uid":170666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:55:41.000Z","msg":"第2集開始"},{"pid":"ab0bbe4cba5dfd54881d368f2be22182ea8fef24","tid":2369931,"uid":170666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T15:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5EmLDud.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5EmLDud.png&h=b49fdd68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df7045a7cffc7fd591c14fc768c38209dbda17f4","tid":2369931,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ozg7RXs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fozg7RXs.png&h=79ee65cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMy name is Tracey <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncy.